<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.4">
<l>teruviṉ kaṇiṉṟiḷa vāycci mārkaḷait tīmaicey yātē</l>
<l>maruvun tamaṉaka mumcīr mālai maṇamkamaḻ kiṉṟa</l>
<l>puruvam karuṅkuḻal neṟṟi polinta mukiṟkaṉṟu pōlē</l>
<l>yuruvama ḻakiya nampī yukantivai cūṭṭanī vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Don’t stand in the street doing harm to the young herdesses,</l>
<l>Like a cloud[-coloured] calf whose forehead is rich</l>
<l rend="indent">with fragrant eyebrows and curly black hair –</l>
<l rend="indent">beautiful, shapely Prince!</l>
<l>Come joyfully so that [I can] adorn you</l>
<l>with these beautiful garlands of marjoram and</l>
<l>trumpet flower which emit a [sweet] fragrance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
